title: Gary Numan, Live From The 2013 Mt. Oasis Festival
description: Singer and composer Gary Numan is considered a pioneer of synth-based electronic music who has often featured a heavy rock influence. For this special Mountain Oasis set, Numan performed a number of his classic hits, as well as new tracks from his 2013 album, Splinter. I Am Dust Films The Fall Everything Comes Down To This Here In The Black The Calling Down In The Park Splinter When The Sky Bleeds, He Will Come Lost Cars We're The Unforgiven Love Hurt Bleed My Last Day Metal A Prayer For The Unborn
